# Tessl-generated artifacts (regenerated by `tessl install`; analogous to
# node_modules). `tessl.json` is the committed manifest; the vendored
# content under `.tessl/tiles/` and the per-agent skill surfaces below
# all come from it.
.tessl/tiles/
.tessl/RULES.md
.claude/skills/tessl__*
# Claude Code runtime state: the scheduled-tasks lock holds the host
# agent's pid + session id, local permission overrides belong to the
# developer's workstation, not the repo. Kept out of git AND out of
# the private→public sync (see scripts/sync-to-public.sh excludes).
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
.agents/
.codex/
.github/skills/
AGENTS.md

agents-sdk-docs
scripts/heartbeat-external.conf
scripts/heartbeat-external.state
._*
